						</div>
						<div class="content content-4">
							<p>Facilitate the exchange of exemplary teaching methods for anatomy and cell biology by integrating contemporary educational technologies and methodologies. Investigate the ethical considerations associated with the utilization of human and animal specimens in anatomical research. Scrutinize the ethical, legal, and social implications stemming from progress in anatomy, cell biology, and biotechnology. Additionally, examine the incorporation of technology to elevate anatomy education, encompassing virtual dissections and 3D models.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="content content-5">
							<p>Highlight the historical and contemporary connections between art and life, such as medical illustration and anatomical art.</p>
